    <title type="html"><![CDATA[TDD in Common Lisp: recursive yak-shaving]]></title>
    <link href="http://code-and-cocktails.herokuapp.com/blog/2013/12/25/tdd-in-common-lisp-recursive-yak-shaving/"/>
